_sText:
At last, Version 1 of skyhigh is out. 

Slots : 40.

This version includes :
- Minor Barricade Rooms.
- Alot of Brushwork.
- Advanced hiding area's.
- More Hiding areas.
- Camping Areas.
- Lighting.
- Giant Slides.
- Extended Tower.
- Simple Brushwork Stuctures to camp on.
- Breakable stairs.
- Teleporters to get ontop of the high walls.
- Working Water, also at slides to help you slow down.
- Good FPS, not the best.
---------------------------------------------

Since this is only version 1, expect more changes, and additions in upcoming version 2, of zm_orange_skyhigh!

Have fun out there!
